# <type>(<scope>): <short summary>
#
# Types: feat fix docs style refactor test ci chore perf build
# Scope: optional, e.g. (auth) (api) (db) (docker) (ci)
#
# Body (optional): explain the WHY, not the WHAT
#
# Examples:
#   feat(auth): add JWT refresh token rotation
#   fix(db): use parameterized queries to prevent SQL injection
#   chore(ci): upgrade actions/checkout from v3 to v4
#
# Rules:
#   - Subject line <= 72 chars
#   - Use imperative mood ("add" not "added")
#   - No period at end of subject
#   - Reference issues: Closes #123
